Thence N 32° 00′ W, 410 meters to corner 10, concrete monument, identical to corner FZ No. 130;

Thence N 72° 00′ W, 330 meters to corner 11, concrete monument, identical to corner FZ No. 129;

Thence N 55° 00′ W, 260 meters to corner 12, concrete monument, identical to corner FZ No. 128;

Thence N 20° 00′ W, 340 meters to corner 13, concrete monument, identical to corner FZ No. 127;

Thence N 41° 00′ W, 400 meters to corner 14, concrete monument, identical to corner FZ No. 126;

Thence N 48° 00′ E, 480 meters to corner 15, concrete monument, identical to corner FZ No. 125;

Thence N 41° 00′ E, 670 meters to corner 16, concrete monument, identical to corner FZ No. 124;

Thence N 69° 00′ E, 660 meters to corner 17, concrete monument, identical to corner FZ No. 123;

Thence S 81° 00′ E, 390 meters to corner 18, concrete monument, identical to corner FZ No. 122;

Thence S 40° 00′ E, 410 meters to corner 1, the point of beginning; containing an area of FOUR HUNDRED THIRTY TWO (432) hectares, more or less.

The Department of Environment and Natural Resources shall administer and manage the reservation thru its Forest Management Bureau in coordination with other agencies of the government with the objective of maintaining its usefulness as source of water for domestic, agriculture and industrial uses, and for other forestry purposes.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 25th day of October, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and ninety one.

(Sgd.) CORAZON C. AQUINO

By the President: (Sgd.) FRANKLIN M. DRILON

